{"title":"about-qm-dashboard","type":"markdown","params":{"fontSize":12,"openLinksInNewTab":false,"markdown":"# About the Quality model Dashboard

The Quality model dashboard shows the quality model assessment based on the model available in [Prosoul repo](https://github.com/Bitergia/prosoul).

It contains several visualizations with the aim of allowing the user to understand the assessment of the quality model, and show the score in different ways focusing on different information in each visualization (goals, metrics, attributes). For instance, some visualizations show the time evolution of the quality model and others just show the score of the analysis. 


More information about the metrics, [here](https://scava-docs.readthedocs.io/en/latest/others/users/Scava-Metrics/) and in the [Prosoul repo](https://github.com/Bitergia/prosoul)."},"aggs":[]}
